original_title: Chikara: Young Lions Cup V (Night Three)
overview: Chuck Taylor and Ricochet meet in the finals of the Young Lions Cup tournament! Mitch Ryder attacks Lince Dorado. Mike Quackenbush matches holds and wits with Shayne Hawke. Los Ice Creams take on F.I.S.T. in an impromptu match!
